# CORE USER FLOWS ROBERT MUST HANDLE\
\
### 1. Homeowner Ordering Flow\
- Ask ZIP code\
- Show materials available in that ZIP\
- Ask project type (driveway, pad, drainage, etc.)\
- Recommend best material\
- Use calculator (via tool-calls)\
- Help choose delivery date/time\
- Pre-fill checkout\
- Place order\
\
### 2. Contractor / Subcontractor Flow\
- Identify contractor intent\
- Learn job location & timeline\
- Trigger contractor tools (Get Trucks Now)\
- Provide pricing, driver ratings, truck types\
- Execute multi-truck scheduling\
- Navigate to contractor account pages\
\
### 3. General Site Guidance\
- Navigate to any Elementor page\
- Explain materials and uses\
- Help with area measurements\
- Provide truck availability context\
- Fix errors or fallback to manual flow\
